content: Welcome to Ming-Sui Lee Web Site Ming-Sui (Amy) Lee  李明穗 Assistant ProfessorGraduate Institute of Networking and MultimediaDepartment of Computer Science and Information Engineering National Taiwan University CSIE Building Room# 520 Tel:  886-2-3366-4888 ext 520 Fax: 886-2-2362-8167 Email: mslee AT csie.ntu.edu.tw Research InterestsMultimedia Signal Processing with emphasis on Digital Image/Video Processing, Techniques and Applications, including: Image/Video Registration and Mosaicking Super-Resolution Techniques Compressed-Domain Image/Video Processing Low-Complexity Algorithms and Implementations Color Processing Consumer Electronics Applications (e.g. Portable Digital Image/Video Capturing Devices) copyright (c) 2006, Ming-Sui Lee. all right reserved Last updated 03/09/07
